==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hello
<hw>Hel*lo"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>interj. & n.</pos> <def>An
exclamation used as a greeting, to call attention, as an exclamation of
surprise, or to encourage one. This variant of <er>Halloo</er> and
<er>Holloo</er> has become the dominant form. In the United States, it
is the most common greeting used in answering a telephone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hellward</ent>⟦br⟧
